WEBVTT

01:41:11.025 --> 01:41:13.442
So, this is where you murdered everyone?

01:41:13.984 --> 01:41:14.525
Yes.

01:41:15.525 --> 01:41:16.567
This is my kingdom.

01:41:16.775 --> 01:41:17.817
I am the king here.

01:41:19.192 --> 01:41:21.442
I did not select this place
by coincidence.

01:41:22.192 --> 01:41:23.984
This place has its unique specialty.

01:41:24.984 --> 01:41:25.734
You know what?

01:41:25.775 --> 01:41:28.359
When I am about to kill someone,
they will scream for help right?

01:41:28.442 --> 01:41:30.317
That sound will bounce
of from all these walls,

01:41:30.359 --> 01:41:32.817
and falls on my ears and
hits the right spot on head!
